Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}人类 强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}问谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}想 问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}谁？强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs32}{\fad(0,300)}希望
